    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just that the advice everyone gives feels so hollow. \"it gets better\" or \"just reach out\"... it doesn't change the fact that the house is empty. i'm just so tired of fighting to feel okay when everything feels so fundamentally broken. i just want the noise in my head to stop. i just want it to be still.",
